    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A coarse, hard-wearing cotton fabric made from colored yarn, often blue in color, and typically used to make work clothes. Later, a heavy cotton fabric similar to this, particularly North American blue denim.</Note_Text>
